{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Inhaltskategorien","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><span class=\"seoSummary\">Für jedes HTML-Element gibt es Regeln, welche definieren, welchen Inhalt es hat. Diese Regeln sind zu Inhaltsmodellen gruppiert, welche für mehrere Elemente gelten. Jedes HTML-Element gehört zu null oder einem oder mehreren Inhaltsmodellen, von welchen jedes die Regeln bestimmt, welche der Inhalt des Elementes in einem gültigen HTML-Document befolgen muss.</span></p>\n\n<p>Es gibt drei Typen von Inhaltskategorien:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Hauptinhaltskategorien(engl. <code>main content categories</code>), welche Inhaltsregeln beschreiben, welche bei vielen Elementen gültig sind;</li>\n <li>Formzusammenhängende Inhaltskategorien(engl. <code>form-related content categories</code>), welche Inhaltsregeln beschreiben, welche für formzusammenhängende Elemente gelten;</li>\n <li>Spezifische Inhaltskategorien(engl.<code> specific content categories</code>), welche seltene Kategorien beschreiben, welche nur für wenige Elemente gelten, manchmal nur in einem spezifischen Context.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div style=\"width: 50%;\" id=\"sect1\"><a href=\"/@api/deki/files/6244/=Content_categories_venn.png\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\"><img alt=\"Content_categories_venn.png\" class=\"default internal\" src=\"/@api/deki/files/6244/=Content_categories_venn.png?size=webview\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"hauptinhaltskategorien","title":"Hauptinhaltskategorien","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"metadateninhalt","title":"Metadateninhalt","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Elemente, welche zu der <em>Metadata</em>inhaltscategorie(engl.<em>metadata content category</em>) gehören, verändern die Präsentation oder das Verhalten des Restes des Documentes, stellen Links zu anderen Documenten ein, oder enthalten andere <em>out-of-band</em>-Information.</p>\n\n<p>Elemente, die zu dieser Kategorie gehören, sind <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/base\"><code>&lt;base&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>&lt;command&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/link\"><code>&lt;link&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meta\"><code>&lt;meta&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/noscript\"><code>&lt;noscript&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> und <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"fließender_inhalt","title":"<a name=\"fließender_Inhalt\">Fließender Inhalt</a>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Elemente, die zu der Kategorie des fließenden Inhaltes(engl.<em>flow content category</em> gehören, enthalten typischerweise Text oder eingebetteten Inhalt. Sie sind: <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr\"><code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/audio\"><code>&lt;audio&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/b\"><code>&lt;b&gt;</code></a>,<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/bdo\"><code>&lt;bdo&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/bdi\"><code>&lt;bdi&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/blockquote\"><code>&lt;blockquote&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/br\"><code>&lt;br&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/cite\"><code>&lt;cite&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/code\"><code>&lt;code&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>&lt;command&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/data\"><code>&lt;data&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/datalist\"><code>&lt;datalist&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/del\"><code>&lt;del&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details\"><code>&lt;details&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dfn\"><code>&lt;dfn&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dl\"><code>&lt;dl&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/em\"><code>&lt;em&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/embed\"><code>&lt;embed&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/fieldset\"><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/figure\"><code>&lt;figure&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h2&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h3&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h4&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h5&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hgroup\"><code>&lt;hgroup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hr\"><code>&lt;hr&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/i\"><code>&lt;i&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/iframe\"><code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ins\"><code>&lt;ins&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/kbd\"><code>&lt;kbd&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label\"><code>&lt;label&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/main\"><code>&lt;main&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/map\"><code>&lt;map&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/mark\"><code>&lt;mark&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/menu\"><code>&lt;menu&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/noscript\"><code>&lt;noscript&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object\"><code>&lt;object&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ol\"><code>&lt;ol&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/output\"><code>&lt;output&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/p\"><code>&lt;p&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/pre\"><code>&lt;pre&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress\"><code>&lt;progress&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/q\"><code>&lt;q&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ruby\"><code>&lt;ruby&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/s\"><code>&lt;s&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/samp\"><code>&lt;samp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/small\"><code>&lt;small&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> und Text.</p>\n\n<p>Einige wenige Elemente gehören zu dieser Kategorie, aber nur, wenn eine specifische Bedingung erfüllt ist:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/area\"><code>&lt;area&gt;</code></a>, falls es ein Nachfolger eines <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/map\"><code>&lt;map&gt;</code></a>-Elementes ist</li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/link\"><code>&lt;link&gt;</code></a>, falls das <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-itemprop\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes#itemprop\"><strong>itemprop</strong></a>-Attribut geschrieben ist</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meta\"><code>&lt;meta&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, falls das <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-itemprop\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes#itemprop\"><strong>itemprop</strong></a>-Attribut geschrieben ist</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, falls das <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>scoped</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>-Attribut geschrieben ist</li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"Fließender Inhalt"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"unterteilender_inhalt","title":"Unterteilender Inhalt","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Elemente, die zu dem <em>sectioninig-content</em>-Modell gehören, erstellen eine <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Sections_and_Outlines_of_an_HTML5_document\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">Section in der laufenden Outline</a>, welche das Aussehen eines <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a>-Elementes , <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a>-Elementes, und <a href=\"#heading_content\" title=\"#heading content\">Überschrifteninhaltes</a> definiert.</p>\n\n<p>Elemente, die zu dieser Categorie gehören, sind <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a> und <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><em>Notiz:</em> Nicht dieses Modell mit der <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Sections_and_Outlines_of_an_HTML5_document#sectioning_root\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">Sectionierende-Wurzel</a>-Kategorie(engl.<em>sectioning root category</em>, welche ihren Inhalt von der regularen Outline isoliert, verwechseln.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"überschrifteninhalt","title":"Überschrifteninhalt","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Überschrifteninhalt definiert den Titel einer Section, dabei gibt es keinen Unterschied, ob es mit einem expliciten <a href=\"#sectionierender_inhalt\" title=\"#Sectionierender Inhalt\">sectionierenden Inhalt</a> gekennzeichnet oder implicite durch den Überschrifteninhalt selbst definiert ist.</p>\n\n<p>Elemente, die zu dieser Categorie gehören, sind <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h2&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h3&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h4&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h5&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code></a> und <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hgroup\"><code>&lt;hgroup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\">\n<p><em>Notiz:</em> Obwohl es meistens Überschrifteninhalt enthält, ist <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a> selbst kein Überschrifteninhalt.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gestaltender_inhalt","title":"Gestaltender Inhalt","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Gestaltender Inhalt definiert den Text und das Markup, welche er enthält. Folgen von phrasierendem Inhalt sind Paragraphen.</p>\n\n<p>Elemente, die zu dieser Categorie gehören, sind <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr\"><code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/audio\"><code>&lt;audio&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/b\"><code>&lt;b&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/bdo\"><code>&lt;bdo&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/br\"><code>&lt;br&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/cite\"><code>&lt;cite&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/code\"><code>&lt;code&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>&lt;command&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/datalist\"><code>&lt;datalist&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dfn\"><code>&lt;dfn&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/em\"><code>&lt;em&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/embed\"><code>&lt;embed&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/i\"><code>&lt;i&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/iframe\"><code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/kbd\"><code>&lt;kbd&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label\"><code>&lt;label&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/mark\"><code>&lt;mark&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/noscript\"><code>&lt;noscript&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object\"><code>&lt;object&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/output\"><code>&lt;output&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress\"><code>&lt;progress&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/q\"><code>&lt;q&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ruby\"><code>&lt;ruby&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/samp\"><code>&lt;samp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/small\"><code>&lt;small&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> und einfacher Text (welcher nicht nur aus Leerzeichen-Zeichen besteht).</p>\n\n<p>Einige andere Elemente, die zu dieser Categorie gehören, aber nur, falls eine bestimmte Condition erfüllt ist:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a>, falls es nur phrasierenden Inhalt enthält</li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/area\"><code>&lt;area&gt;</code></a>, falls es das Descendens eines <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/map\"><code>&lt;map&gt;</code></a>-Elementes ist</li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/del\"><code>&lt;del&gt;</code></a>, falls es nur phrasierenden Inhalt enthält</li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ins\"><code>&lt;ins&gt;</code></a>, falls es nur phrasierenden Inhalt enthält</li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/link\"><code>&lt;link&gt;</code></a>, falls das <a href=\"/de/docs/HTML/Globale_Attribute#itemprop\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\"><strong>itemprop</strong></a>-Attribut geschrieben ist</li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/map\"><code>&lt;map&gt;</code></a>, falls es nur phrasierenden Inhalt enthält</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meta\"><code>&lt;meta&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, falls das <a href=\"/de/docs/HTML/Globale_Attribute#itemprop\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\"><strong>itemprop</strong></a>-Attribut geschrieben ist.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eingebetter_inhalt","title":"Eingebetter Inhalt","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Eingebetteter Inhalt importiert eine andere Ressource oder gibt Inhalt einer anderen Markup-Sprache oder Namensraumes in das Document ein. Elemente in dieser Categorie sind: <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/audio\"><code>&lt;audio&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/embed\"><code>&lt;embed&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/iframe\"><code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code></a>, <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object\"><code>&lt;object&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"interaktiver_inhalt","title":"<a name=\"interactiver_Inhalt\">Interaktiver Inhalt</a>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Interaktiver Inhalt enthält Elemente, die speziell für Interaktionen mit dem Benutzer gedacht sind. Folgende Elemente geöhren zu dieser Kategorie: <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details\"><code>&lt;details&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/embed\"><code>&lt;embed&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/iframe\"><code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label\"><code>&lt;label&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, and <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.<br>\n Einige Elemente sind nur unter spezifischen Conditionen in dieser Categorie:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/audio\"><code>&lt;audio&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, falls das <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/audio\"><code>controls</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>-Attribut geschrieben ist</li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code></a>, falls das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img#attr-usemap\"><code>usemap</code></a>-Attribut geschrieben ist</li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>, falls das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input#attr-type\"><code>type</code></a>-Attribut nicht im versteckten Status ist.</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/menu\"><code>&lt;menu&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, falls das <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/menu\"><code>type</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>-Attribut im Toolbar-Status ist</li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object\"><code>&lt;object&gt;</code></a>, falls das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object#attr-usemap\"><code>usemap</code></a>-Attribut geschrieben ist</li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a>, falls das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video#attr-controls\"><code>controls</code></a>-Attribut geschrieben ist.</li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"Interaktiver Inhalt"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"fühlbarer_inhalt","title":"Fühlbarer Inhalt","isH3":true,"content":"<p>&nbsp;A content is palpable when it's neither empty nor hidden. Elements whose model is flow content or phrasing content should have at least one node which is palpable.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"formularbezogener_inhalt","title":"Formularbezogener Inhalt","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Formularassoziierter Inhalt umfasst Elemente mit einem Formularbezeichner, welcher durch ein Formularattribut&nbsp;verfügbar gemacht wird. Ein Formularbezeichner ist entweder das enthaltende <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Element oder das Element, dessen ID im Formularattribut angegeben ist.</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/fieldset\"><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label\"><code>&lt;label&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object\"><code>&lt;object&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/output\"><code>&lt;output&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress\"><code>&lt;progress&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>This category contains several sub-categories:</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"gelistet\"><a id=\"Formular_gelistet\" name=\"Formular_gelistet\">gelistet</a></dt>\n <dd>Elements that are listed in the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormElement/elements\" title=\"DOM/form.elements\">form.elements</a> and fieldset.elements IDL&nbsp;collections. Contains <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/fieldset\"><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object\"><code>&lt;object&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/output\"><code>&lt;output&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, and <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"bezeichenbar\"><a id=\"Formular_bezeichenbar\" name=\"Formular_bezeichenbar\">bezeichenbar</a></dt>\n <dd>Elements that can be associated with <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label\"><code>&lt;label&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> elements. Contains <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/output\"><code>&lt;output&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress\"><code>&lt;progress&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, and <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"abschickbar\"><a id=\"Formular_abschickbar\" name=\"Formular_abschickbar\">abschickbar</a></dt>\n <dd>Elements that can be used for constructing the form data set when the form is submitted. Contains <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object\"><code>&lt;object&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, and <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"zurücksetzbar\"><a id=\"Formular_zurücksetzbar\" name=\"Formular_zurücksetzbar\">zurücksetzbar</a></dt>\n <dd>Elements that can be affected when a form is reset. Contains <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/output\"><code>&lt;output&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>,<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, and <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"transparentes_inhaltsmodell","title":"Transparentes Inhaltsmodell","isH3":false,"content":"<p>If an element has a transparent content model, then its contents must be structured such that they would be valid HTML 5, even if the transparent element were removed and replaced by the child elements.</p>\n\n<p>For example, the <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/del\"><code>&lt;del&gt;</code></a> and <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ins\"><code>&lt;ins&gt;</code></a> elements are transparent:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;p&gt;We hold these truths to be &lt;del&gt;&lt;em&gt;sacred &amp;amp; undeniable&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/del&gt; &lt;ins&gt;self-evident&lt;/ins&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\n</pre>\n\n<p>If those elements were removed, this fragment would still be valid HTML (if not correct English).</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;p&gt;We hold these truths to be &lt;em&gt;sacred &amp;amp; undeniable&lt;/em&gt; self-evident.&lt;/p&gt;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"andere_inhaltsmodelle","title":"Andere Inhaltsmodelle","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Sectioning root.</p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Hauptinhaltskategorien","id":"hauptinhaltskategorien"},{"text":"Transparentes Inhaltsmodell","id":"transparentes_inhaltsmodell"},{"text":"Andere Inhaltsmodelle","id":"andere_inhaltsmodelle"}],"summary":"Für jedes HTML-Element gibt es Regeln, welche definieren, welchen Inhalt es hat. Diese Regeln sind zu Inhaltsmodellen gruppiert, welche für mehrere Elemente gelten. Jedes HTML-Element gehört zu null oder einem oder mehreren Inhaltsmodellen, von welchen jedes die Regeln bestimmt, welche der Inhalt des Elementes in einem gültigen HTML-Document befolgen muss.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Content categories","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Categorías de contenido","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Catégories de contenu","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"コンテンツカテゴリー","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"콘텐츠 카테고리","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Categorias de conteúdo","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Категории контента","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"内容分类","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"內容類型","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/guide/html/content_categories","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/guide/html/content_categories/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/Guide","title":"Web-Entwickler Leitfäden"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories","title":"Inhaltskategorien"}],"pageTitle":"Inhaltskategorien - Web-Entwickler Leitfäden | MDN","noIndexing":false}}